          <mxGeometry x="75" y="520" width="370" height="58" as="geometry" />
          <UserObject label="&lt;b style='color:#94A3B8'&gt;Resilience:&lt;/b&gt; MASS auto-restarts (restart:always). On persistent failure, signed human override logged to PeaRL. Gate never silently bypassed." />
